      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 2,
      "text": "The Goethe B2 Schreiben (Writing) module takes 75 minutes total. You write two texts. You can start with either task. Only texts on the answer sheet are graded. Write with a blue or black pen. No aids (dictionaries, phones, mobile devices) are allowed."
    },
